1301
01:45:11.311 --> 01:45:14.231
<i>Gentlemen, start your engines.</i>

1302
01:45:14.815 --> 01:45:15.649
Let's go.

1303
01:45:16.692 --> 01:45:19.653
<i>One of the world's most iconic races,
the Le Mans 24,</i>

1304
01:45:19.736 --> 01:45:23.240
<i>stands just moments away
at the Circuit de la Sarthe.</i>

1305
01:45:23.323 --> 01:45:26.493
<i>And, Chenny, so many great stories
the length and breadth of this field,</i>

1306
01:45:26.577 --> 01:45:29.204
<i>but for me the one that's taking
my focus right now</i>

1307
01:45:29.288 --> 01:45:31.415
<i>is the incredible story at Nissan.</i>

1308
01:45:31.498 --> 01:45:35.586
<i>Is the last chance the SIM racers get
in professional motorsport?</i>

1309
01:45:35.669 --> 01:45:37.254
<i>There's an awful lot of pressure
on their shoulders.</i>

1310
01:45:37.337 --> 01:45:40.048
Nobody wins this thing
on the first lap, okay?

1311
01:45:41.258 --> 01:45:45.053
You make your day, survive the night,
you live to fight tomorrow.

1312
01:45:48.891 --> 01:45:49.892
Good luck.

1313
01:46:40.692 --> 01:46:43.487
<i>As the cars now leave the grid
for the formation lap</i>

1314
01:46:43.570 --> 01:46:45.656
<i>here at the Circuit de la Sarthe,</i>

1315
01:46:45.739 --> 01:46:49.284
<i>we are just moments away
from the start of this iconic race.</i>

1316
01:47:11.265 --> 01:47:14.810
<i>We're underway already and, listen,
you've gotta be smart going into turn one.</i>

1317
01:47:14.893 --> 01:47:17.437
<i>The tires are still cold.
Contact! Contact in the back!</i>

1318
01:47:17.521 --> 01:47:19.356
<i>We've seen the BMW and the Aston Martin--</i>

1319
01:47:35.497 --> 01:47:38.083
<i>Okay, here we go.</i>

1320
01:47:38.166 --> 01:47:40.127
Mulsanne Straight.

1321
01:47:40.210 --> 01:47:43.463
<i>You could hit a high of 340 kph here.</i>

1322
01:47:43.547 --> 01:47:46.008
<i>You gotta build in enough time
to brake before chicane one.</i>

1323
01:47:46.091 --> 01:47:49.219
Yes, yes. Okay.
I've done this a thousand times.

1324
01:47:49.303 --> 01:47:51.054
<i>Well, not in reality.</i>

1325
01:47:51.138 --> 01:47:52.639
Watch your speed.

1326
01:47:59.771 --> 01:48:02.149
<i>Into the first chicane,
around the outside,</i>

1327
01:48:02.232 --> 01:48:05.068
<i>and it's a lovely move put on there
by Jann Mardenborough.</i>

1328
01:48:05.903 --> 01:48:08.947
<i>Watch those GT3s.
You're way faster than them.</i>

1329
01:48:13.744 --> 01:48:15.037
I see Schulin.

1330
01:48:15.120 --> 01:48:16.997
<i>Come on, Jann! Stay on him!</i>

1331
01:48:21.251 --> 01:48:23.962
<i>On your left!
Ferrari's too slow. Watch out!</i>

1332
01:48:24.046 --> 01:48:24.963
No, no, no. No!

1333
01:48:27.090 --> 01:48:30.385
<i>He gets tapped by the Ferrari!
Schulin up in the air!</i>

1334
01:48:37.976 --> 01:48:39.186
Is he okay?!

1335
01:48:55.619 --> 01:48:58.288
{\an8}What's he saying? Was it Jann?

1336
01:49:02.084 --> 01:49:05.003
<i>Schulin! Get out, get out, get out!</i>

1337
01:49:06.755 --> 01:49:08.924
<i>Schulin climbs out of the car.</i>

1338
01:49:09.007 --> 01:49:11.760
<i>Making his way out, and that's good
to see from the fire marshals.</i>

1339
01:49:12.636 --> 01:49:14.513
<i>Safety car's out on the track.</i>

1340
01:49:20.227 --> 01:49:21.436
<i>Stay focused.</i>

1341
01:49:22.312 --> 01:49:25.440
All right, they're pulling him out.
He seems all right. He seems all right.

1342
01:49:26.275 --> 01:49:29.236
<i>After that impact,
it's a miracle the car is in one piece</i>

1343
01:49:29.319 --> 01:49:30.988
<i>and the driver could walk away.</i>

1344
01:49:33.991 --> 01:49:35.701
Get behind that safety car.

1345
01:49:43.125 --> 01:49:45.127
<i>Okay, keep your head in, all right? Focus.</i>

1346
01:49:52.885 --> 01:49:56.638
<i>All right, safety's out, race back on.
Let's go, let's go!</i>

1347
01:49:56.722 --> 01:49:57.723
<i>Come on!</i>

1348
01:50:01.768 --> 01:50:02.978
Come on, you hear me?

1349
01:50:05.314 --> 01:50:08.317
<i>Hey, buddy? Hey. Hey, Jann?</i>

1350
01:50:08.400 --> 01:50:11.153
Hey, stay with me.
Stay with me, okay? Stay with me.

1351
01:50:12.446 --> 01:50:15.532
<i>Look, safety's left, okay?
We gotta make up some time.</i>

1352
01:50:16.283 --> 01:50:17.117
<i>Jann.</i>

1353
01:50:19.119 --> 01:50:20.913
Jann, talk to me, pal.

1354
01:50:20.996 --> 01:50:22.581
Jann. Hey, hey, hey.

1355
01:50:22.664 --> 01:50:24.041
Hey, Jann.

1356
01:50:24.124 --> 01:50:26.793
<i>Is it a car problem
or is it a head issue, Will?</i>

1357
01:50:26.877 --> 01:50:30.005
<i>It would be early for anything
to be wrong with that car,</i>

1358
01:50:30.088 --> 01:50:31.423
<i>which has shown good pace.</i>

1359
01:50:37.262 --> 01:50:38.305
Bitch.

1360
01:50:39.473 --> 01:50:40.891
Shit.

1361
01:50:40.974 --> 01:50:42.017
<i>Jack!</i>

1362
01:50:42.100 --> 01:50:43.727
We need to bring him in.

1363
01:50:45.771 --> 01:50:47.147
Then do something.

1364
01:50:47.231 --> 01:50:49.566
Just get his head back in this game.

1365
01:51:07.543 --> 01:51:08.377
Dude.

1366
01:51:09.378 --> 01:51:11.380
Dude, what the hell? Turn it off.

1367
01:51:15.926 --> 01:51:17.219
Turn it off!

1368
01:51:17.302 --> 01:51:19.096
<i>Now! Turn it off!</i>

1369
01:51:19.847 --> 01:51:23.100
Okay, let me just--
Oh, God, I don't know how to--

1370
01:51:23.183 --> 01:51:25.310
I told you,
I don't how to work these things.

1371
01:51:26.061 --> 01:51:29.147
<i>Shit, Jack, turn it off now!</i>

1372
01:51:30.482 --> 01:51:31.692
Shit.

1373
01:51:32.401 --> 01:51:33.610
Off.

1374
01:51:40.576 --> 01:51:41.577
You mad, bro?

1375
01:51:42.119 --> 01:51:43.662
Fucking yes!

1376
01:51:43.745 --> 01:51:45.414
Yes, I'm mad!

1377
01:51:45.497 --> 01:51:46.832
Yeah!

1378
01:51:46.915 --> 01:51:49.668
Well, get mad! It's about time!

1379
01:51:49.751 --> 01:51:52.212
Come on! Get in the fight!

1380
01:51:52.296 --> 01:51:54.131
I know you're scared.

1381
01:51:54.798 --> 01:51:56.341
I've been scared.

1382
01:51:57.050 --> 01:52:00.387
Whether you like it or not,
you are in this race.

1383
01:52:00.470 --> 01:52:04.349
So you take all that Kenny G anger
and you unleash it!

1384
01:52:04.433 --> 01:52:05.976
<i>You hear me?</i>

1385
01:52:06.059 --> 01:52:07.269
Yes, sir.

1386
01:52:07.352 --> 01:52:09.313
<i>All right.</i>

1387
01:52:09.396 --> 01:52:10.397
<i>Go get 'em!</i>

1388
01:52:22.534 --> 01:52:24.953
<i>It's like he suddenly remembered
he was a racing driver.</i>

1389
01:52:25.037 --> 01:52:29.917
<i>Absolutely phenomenal display
by the debutante here in that Nissan.</i>

1390
01:52:30.000 --> 01:52:31.793
All right, all right.

1391
01:52:36.340 --> 01:52:39.468
All right, coming up on Lotus.
Three seconds ahead.

1392
01:52:42.054 --> 01:52:43.639
<i>Let's make up some ground.</i>

1393
01:52:44.139 --> 01:52:45.724
<i>You have the same power on the straight,</i>

1394
01:52:45.807 --> 01:52:48.435
but if you get in the corner,
you'll be able to pass him, all right?

1395
01:52:49.019 --> 01:52:51.063
Okay, copy. Let me concentrate, old man.

1396
01:52:51.146 --> 01:52:52.731
Yeah, all right. Roger that. Copy.

1397
01:53:10.374 --> 01:53:12.709
Yes! Yes!

1398
01:53:12.793 --> 01:53:16.588
<i>Beautiful stuff from Jann Mardenborough
and from this Nissan team.</i>

1399
01:53:19.967 --> 01:53:21.051
Yes!

1400
01:53:21.718 --> 01:53:22.803
All right.

1401
01:53:23.720 --> 01:53:26.223
Now we only got 150 laps to go.

1402
01:53:26.932 --> 01:53:31.019
<i>He pulled that first stint back,
and Jann Mardenborough into the pits</i>

1403
01:53:31.103 --> 01:53:33.188
<i>for the first driver change for Nissan.</i>

1404
01:53:33.272 --> 01:53:35.148
Fast out there, man. Let's go, Matty!

1405
01:53:35.232 --> 01:53:36.733
Let's go, let's go, let's go!

1406
01:53:41.822 --> 01:53:42.990
Adis!

1407
01:53:44.074 --> 01:53:46.618
<i>As the sun goes down,
it's a whole new ballgame.</i>

1408
01:53:48.745 --> 01:53:49.913
Don't rush it.

1409
01:53:49.997 --> 01:53:51.748
<i>I'm gonna take the inside line, Jack.</i>

1410
01:53:54.251 --> 01:53:55.669
-Yeah! Yes!
-Yo, son!

1411
01:53:55.752 --> 01:53:56.670
Yes!

1412
01:53:56.753 --> 01:53:59.214
-Maybe you boys can actually drive.
-You know we can drive.

1413
01:53:59.298 --> 01:54:00.924
<i>Oh, yeah, jury's still out.</i>

1414
01:54:08.891 --> 01:54:09.892
<i>You're in P-9.</i>

1415
01:54:13.645 --> 01:54:17.232
Get tires ready. Here we go.
Let's go, let's go, let's go.

1416
01:54:19.234 --> 01:54:20.986
<i>All leaders are on full wets.</i>

1417
01:54:35.042 --> 01:54:36.793
<i>Jann's doing great, isn't he?</i>

1418
01:54:36.877 --> 01:54:39.505
-Do you think so?
-You joking? Mate, he's razing it!

1419
01:54:39.588 --> 01:54:41.048
I can't believe it. He's doing amazing.

1420
01:54:42.174 --> 01:54:44.885
Nice and softly, nice and smooth.

1421
01:55:38.856 --> 01:55:39.898
<i>Hey, boys!</i>

1422
01:55:39.982 --> 01:55:41.692
-How are you boys doing?
-Hey, man.

1423
01:55:41.775 --> 01:55:43.861
-Jann, how you feeling?
-I feel good.

1424
01:55:43.944 --> 01:55:45.195
-Yeah?
-Yeah.

1425
01:55:46.071 --> 01:55:47.072
Rest up.

1426
01:56:00.419 --> 01:56:05.215
<i>First light at Circuit de la Sarthe
at the 24 Hours of Le Mans.</i>

1427
01:56:05.299 --> 01:56:06.758
Here you are, Audrey. Got you a coffee.

1428
01:56:06.842 --> 01:56:08.135
-Thanks.
-No worries.

1429
01:56:08.886 --> 01:56:10.137
How's it looking?

1430
01:56:10.220 --> 01:56:13.849
In fourth, but Antonio is losing ground.

1431
01:56:13.932 --> 01:56:15.267
Not a lot of time left.

1432
01:56:15.809 --> 01:56:18.353
<i>Yeah,
Antonio Cruz clearly struggling there.</i>

1433
01:56:27.446 --> 01:56:28.864
-Hey.
-Hey.

1434
01:56:28.947 --> 01:56:31.658
Antonio's cramping up.
