1450
01:57:18.580 --> 01:57:20.958
-Where's the spare? Where's the spare?
-Are you shitting me?!

1451
01:57:26.046 --> 01:57:27.798
Oh, my God.

1452
01:57:27.881 --> 01:57:28.966
Come on!

1453
01:57:29.049 --> 01:57:31.844
<i>Look at that, it's Jack Salter
