You see, the other guys,
they follow that line.

1460
01:58:42.956 --> 01:58:46.793
So if I go wide like this,

1461
01:58:47.461 --> 01:58:48.921
sometimes I beat them.

1462
01:58:49.004 --> 01:58:49.838
Like that.

