01:59:03.560 --> 01:59:04.561
Yeah, I'm listening.

1465
01:59:04.645 --> 01:59:09.358
The whole point of this thing was
to show that <i>GT</i> drivers can drive.

1466
01:59:09.441 --> 01:59:12.444
<i>Okay? I know this track. I know the lines.</i>

1467
01:59:12.528 --> 01:59:15.781
The line is not optimal.
